Package: df2table
Title: Generate Survey Table Shells from Labelled Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Arthur",
           family = "Shaw",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jashaw2002@gmail.com")
Description: Programmatically generate table shells for survey-style tabulations 
    using labelled data. Separates table structure from data computation, 
    supporting hierarchical row groupings and flexible column definitions 
    with integration to 'gt' and 'flextable' rendering engines.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
